  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time for a climb! Take your prehistoric pets on a tower conquering adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb alone or compete with other players in asynchronous multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mighty mammoth and his friends are ready to conquer the spiral stairs of trap ridden castle towers. Finish all levels, beat timed challenges, collect coins and unlock perks & cosmetics and race against the best time of other players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/99e9f69ebee0cf9504cee8a1f9032fbd.poster.avif?t=1739889297\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/99e9f69ebee0cf9504cee8a1f9032fbd.webm?t=1739889297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/99e9f69ebee0cf9504cee8a1f9032fbd.mp4?t=1739889297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Take chances, but do be careful!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharp spikes, rolling barrels, heavy rocks, falling platforms, fire traps and jumping bombs will block your way, and it is up to your skills, strategy (and of course luck!) to overcome all obstacles. Collect useful tools and abilities on your way up to survive and prosper!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Follow the ghost?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn from the mistakes of your past. You can see the ghostly apparition of your last try on the stairs - follow them, but don't get too comfortable: there is a reason they failed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/3afac8c1c1058deb9999844670f9be9d.poster.avif?t=1739889297\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/3afac8c1c1058deb9999844670f9be9d.webm?t=1739889297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/3afac8c1c1058deb9999844670f9be9d.mp4?t=1739889297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for the challenge ahead?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single player</strong> - challenge yourself in Time trial, or an NPC opponent in Race mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Asynchronous multiplayer</strong> – race against real players in Versus mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perks</strong> - Make most of a randomized perk system each climb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghostly helper</strong> - See your past self to avoid previous mistakes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Colorful kid-friendly graphics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable characters</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time for a climb! Take your prehistoric pets on a tower conquering adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb alone or compete with other players in asynchronous multiplayer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mighty mammoth and his friends are ready to conquer the spiral stairs of trap ridden castle towers. Finish all levels, beat timed challenges, collect coins and unlock perks & cosmetics and race against the best time of other players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/99e9f69ebee0cf9504cee8a1f9032fbd.poster.avif?t=1739889297\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/99e9f69ebee0cf9504cee8a1f9032fbd.webm?t=1739889297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/99e9f69ebee0cf9504cee8a1f9032fbd.mp4?t=1739889297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Take chances, but do be careful!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharp spikes, rolling barrels, heavy rocks, falling platforms, fire traps and jumping bombs will block your way, and it is up to your skills, strategy (and of course luck!) to overcome all obstacles. Collect useful tools and abilities on your way up to survive and prosper!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Follow the ghost?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn from the mistakes of your past. You can see the ghostly apparition of your last try on the stairs - follow them, but don't get too comfortable: there is a reason they failed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/3afac8c1c1058deb9999844670f9be9d.poster.avif?t=1739889297\" width=472 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/3afac8c1c1058deb9999844670f9be9d.webm?t=1739889297\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3446750/extras/3afac8c1c1058deb9999844670f9be9d.mp4?t=1739889297\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready for the challenge ahead?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single player</strong> - challenge yourself in Time trial, or an NPC opponent in Race mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Asynchronous multiplayer</strong> – race against real players in Versus mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Perks</strong> - Make most of a randomized perk system each climb</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghostly helper</strong> - See your past self to avoid previous mistakes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Colorful kid-friendly graphics</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlockable characters</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
